(5, 'Android Developer', 'Company Profile : Indigi Consulting and Solutions Pvt. Ltd is a technology company focused on digital transformation with strategic consultancy and leading enterprise benchmarking and best practices, offering digital transformation including Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP), robotic process automation, and enterprise cloud application implementation. Services include business transformation, enterprise analytics, working capital management and global business services. Indigi Consulting and Solutions also provides dedicated expertise in business strategy, operations, finance, human capital management, strategic sourcing, procurement and information technology. Indigi is the only SAP Partner for SAP ByD, SAP S/4 HANA, SAP Cloud, SAP S/4 HANA Cloud in the entire Northeast India region, and having global presence too.\r\nJob Summary\r\n\r\nWe are looking for an Android & iOS developer responsible for the development and maintenance of applications. Your primary focus will be the development of mobile based applications and their integration with back-end services. Necessary to have commitment to problem solving, sophisticated design, and creating quality products is essential.\r\nDesired Skill Set: net, java, j2ee, oops, swift.', 'India', 'Guwahati, Assam', 'R&D', 'MCA or BE/ B. Tech in CSE/ Information Technology', 'Objective C, Swift , Android , JavaScript, Java, J2EE, Nodejs, Angular JS/React JS, C, NET , React Native e.t.c', '0.6-2 Years', 'Full time / Permanent', 'Responsibilities and Duties:\r\n\r\n- Description : Design, build and configure applications to meet business process and application requirements.\r\n- Must Have Skills : Android Application Development\r\nJob Requirements : Key Responsibilities\r\na. Strong knowledge of OOPS design concepts patterns\r\nb: Experience worked in Java Generic and Collections\r\nc: Experience in creating Activities/Services/inter-process communication in Android\r\nd: Should have knowledge on Asy