(6, 'Web Developer', 'Our Company: \r\nIndigi Consulting and Solutions Pvt. Ltd is a technology company focused on digital transformation with strategic consultancy and leading enterprise benchmarking and best practices, offering digital transformation including Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP), robotic process automation, and enterprise cloud application implementation. Services include business transformation, enterprise analytics, working capital management and global business services. Indigi Consulting and Solutions also provides dedicated expertise in business strategy, operations, finance, human capital management, strategic sourcing, procurement and information technology. Indigi is the only SAP Partner for SAP ByD, SAP S/4 HANA, SAP Cloud, SAP S/4 HANA Cloud in the entire Northeast India region, and having global presence too.', 'India', 'Guwahati, Assam', 'R&D', '•	Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or equivalent', 'HTML, CSS, Laravel PHP, JavaScript, jQuery, Bootstrap (5/4) and AJAX, MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB.', '2 to 3 years', 'Full time / Permanent', 'What you will do:  \r\n•	Determine the structure and design of responsive web pages, striking a balance between functional and aesthetic design\r\n•	Use a variety of programming languages to produce, maintain, and modify website user interfaces for desktops and mobile devices\r\n•	Optimize websites for usability, SEO, performance, scalability, and compliance\r\n•	Implement and support feature sets and third-party integrations\r\n•	Support publishing operations and content management processes\r\n•	Create and maintaining for reusable of codes \r\n•	Develop a comprehensive understanding of our application architecture and how it relates to client needs\r\n•	Working with data base services. \r\n•	Experience performing Database administration or database engineering duties for database internals with experience supporting one of these database platforms: MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB.\r\n•	Developing and design web applications in HTML, CSS, Laravel PHP, JavaScript, jQuery, Bootstrap (5/4) and AJAX. \r\n•	Running stress/load tests to ensure the performance of our infrastructure, identifying areas of improvement\r\n•	Ability to work on dynamic environment.\r\nRequirement:  \r\n•	Experience with JavaScript frameworks (React.js, Angular)\r\n•	Experience in Laravel PHP framework \r\n•	Hands on experience in HTML, CSS Components, jQuery, Bootstrap, AJAX and JavaScript. \r\n•	Also have experience in Database such as MySQL, Maria DB \r\nWhat we will offer you: \r\n•	Best working Culture \r\n•	Local project team and close proximity with the global network (international collaboration)\r\n•	Better opportunity to increase technological skills & professional capability (diversity of projects, languages and technologies)\r\n•	Internal and external training', '2023-02-27 16:26:14', '2023-02-27 16:26:14', 'open', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
