(2, 'SAP CONSULTING & IMPLEMENTATION', 'sap-consulting-implementation', 'SAP Consulting & Implementation services guide organizations through the complete SAP journey—from strategic planning to successful deployment. This includes aligning SAP solutions with business objectives, designing efficient processes, configuring systems, migrating data, training users, and providing post-launch support. By combining expert consulting with hands-on implementation, we help businesses achieve digital transformation, streamline operations, and enable long-term growth.', '2025-04-12_1744439354.png', '<div class=\"stat-card\">\r\n<div class=\"stat-number\">24/7</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-label\">Support</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\r\n<div class=\"stat-number\">99.9%</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-label\">Uptime</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\r\n<div class=\"stat-number\">7+</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-label\">Years Experience</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\r\n<div class=\"stat-number\">50+</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"stat-label\">SAP Experts</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Business Process Analysis &amp; SAP Fitment</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">In-depth evaluation of your existing business processes to identify the most suitable SAP solutions and configurations.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Roadmap Creation &amp; Digital Transformation Planning</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Strategic planning of SAP adoption, transformation phases, and technology upgrades aligned with business goals.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Module-Specific Expertise</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Certified consultants across FI/CO, MM, SD, HCM, and more &mdash; offering best practices and tailored configurations.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">System Architecture &amp; Integration Design</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Designing scalable SAP architecture with seamless integration across systems, third-party apps, and data sources.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Custom Development &amp; Enhancements</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Tailored SAP extensions, reports, and workflows to fit unique business needs and improve operational efficiency.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Compliance &amp; Governance Advisory</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Expert guidance on SAP controls, data governance, and audit readiness to ensure regulatory and security compliance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-card\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"feature-text\">\r\n<h3 class=\"feature-title\">Cloud Readiness &amp; Migration Advisory</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"feature-description\">Assessment and planning for transitioning your SAP landscape to the cloud with minimal risk and maximum benefit.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"duration-container\">\r\n<div class=\"duration-header\">\r\n<h3>Expected Duration</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"duration-options\">\r\n<div class=\"duration-option\">\r\n<h4>Short-Term Consulting Engagements</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Typically 2&ndash;8 weeks for foc