(5, 'Grow With SAP', 'grow-with-sap', 'Scale your business with a ready-to-run cloud ERP solution', '<div class=\"main-content\">\r\n<p class=\"overview-text\" id=\"solution-overview\">GROW witeh SAP S/4HANA is a comprehensive, ready-to-run cloud ERP solution built on SAP S/4HANA Cloud Public Edition. It&#39;s designed to help growing businesses streamline operations, support sustainable growth, and stay agile in a rapidly evolving digital landscape. By leveraging industry best practices and continuous innovation, it enables companies to scale effortlessly and stay ahead of the curve.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"testimonial\">\r\n<p id=\"testimonial-quote\">&quot;GROW with SAP helped us streamline our operations and scale our business without adding complexity. The implementation was smooth, and we saw ROI within months.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p id=\"testimonial-author\">&mdash; Sarah Chen, CFO at GrowTech Solutions</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '\"{\\\"quote\\\":null,\\\"author\\\":null}\"', '<div class=\"highlight-item\">\r\n<div class=\"highlight-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Quick Implementation</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Faster time-to-value with streamlined deployment</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"highlight-item\">\r\n<div class=\"highlight-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Comprehensive Solution</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>All-in-one platform for your business needs</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"highlight-item\">\r\n<div class=\"highlight-icon\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<h4>Data-Driven Insights</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Real-time analytics for better decision making</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"opt-item\"><span>Midsize and fast-growing companies seeking a scalable cloud ERP</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"opt-item\"><span>Businesses new to SAP looking for quick, cost-effective ERP implementation</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"opt-item\"><span>Organizations aiming to standardize and modernize their operations with minimal complexity</span></div>\r