nt\">\r\n<p>AI-driven threat intelligence and monitoring for proactive defense</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"benefit-card\">\r\n<div class=\"benefit-header\">\r\n<h3>Cost-Effective</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"benefit-content\">\r\n<p>Affordable, subscription-based pricing with no heavy infrastructure</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '<div class=\"metric\">\r\n<div class=\"metric-value\" id=\"efficiency-metric\">40%</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Improved threat detection and response time</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"metric\">\r\n<div class=\"metric-value\" id=\"reporting-metric\">60%</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Faster identification of security vulnerabilities</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"metric\">\r\n<div class=\"metric-value\" id=\"cost-metric\">20%</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Reduction in security-related operational costs</p>\r\n</div>', 0, 0, 0, '<p><strong>ReSecurity</strong> provides an end-to-end cybersecurity solution with:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Subscription-based access tailored to your business needs</li>\r\n	<li>AI-powered tools offering 24/7 continuous monitoring</li>\r\n	<li>Automated threat detection and rapid response capabilities</li>\r\n	<li>Proactive risk and vulnerability assessments to strengthen security posture</li>\r\n	<li>Seamless integration with existing infrastructure, ERPs, and cloud services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>By choosing ReSecurity, businesses get an advanced, scalable cybersecurity platform that evolves with emerging threats, ensuring data protection, compliance, and resilience in an ever-changing digital world.</p>', '<div class=\"process-steps\">\r\n<div class=\"process-step\">\r\n<div class=\"step-number\">1</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"step-content\">\r\n<h4>Discovery &amp; Planning</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Assessment of business needs and implementation strategy</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"process-step\">\r\n<div class=\"step-number\">2</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"step-content\">\r\n<h4>Configuration &amp; Setup</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>System c